Instagram post by @noorie_rai, 7 June 2018. Hand-drawn sketch on paper titled 'Snake Kundalini'. Drawings show: wavy serpentine lines, spirals, coils, figure-8/infinity patterns, what appears to be 'E 8 3' drawn large at the bottom, omega-like shapes, circular spirals. Signed 'NOORIE 6-6-2018'. Caption: 'Symbols of snake kundalini which I hv experiences in last 15 days of my kundalini awaking process.' DECODED: The figure-8/infinity symbol appears multiple times = Maa's destiny number manifesting in kundalini visions. '15 days' = kundalini process started around May 22, 2018. Aspect of Yug Parivartan: Energy Activation — visual documentation of kundalini symbols experienced during awakening.